translation[11]{c,v,t}:
  28,60,"Ke kaloku nantoni na eniyiphiweyo, yeyolonwabo (olufutshane) lobu bomi balo mhlaba yaye bungumhombiso ukanti bona uBomi oBuzayo bukuAallâh bubona bulungileyo yaye buya kuhlala bukho ngonaphakade. Kanti aninangqiqo na"
  28,61,"Ingaba lowo Simthembise isithembiso esisesona silungileyo (iPaladesi) aya kusifumana siyinyani uyafana nalowo Simenze ukuba onwabele ubunewunewu beli hlabathi, kunoMhla woVuko, noza kuba ngomnye wabo baya kuvuselwa (ukohlwaywa)"
  28,62,Ngemini Aya kubabiza (uAllâh) Athi “Aphi na kaloku) amahlulelane aM enanidla ngokuwakhankanya?”
  28,63,"Abo ilizwi liya kuzalisekiswa (ngokuchasene nabo) baya kuthi: “Nkosi yethu! Aba ngabo sabalahlekisayo. sabalahlekisa njengoko nathi sasilahlekile.” (Ngoku) thina sazisa ukuba msulwa kwethu (ngokumayela nabo) phambi kwaKho. Yayingesithi abo babebanqula.”"
  28,64,"Kuya kuthiwa (kubo): “Bizani kaloku kuloo mahlulelane enu (nithi ngaka-Allâh), baya kubiza ke kuwo, kodwa akayi kubanika mpendulo, yaye baya kusibona isohlwayo. (baze banqwenele) ukuba akwaba babekhokelelekile"
  28,65,NgeMini (uAllâh) Aya kumemeza kubo Athi; “Mpendulo ni na enayinika abaThunywa (baM)?”
  28,66,"Kodwa iindaba ezingempendulo elungileyo aziyi kucaca kubo ngaloo Mini, yaye abayi kukwazi nokubuzana"
  28,67,"Kodwayenalowowaguqukayo, wakholwa, wenzaubulungisa, uthenjisiwe nguAllâh okokuba uya kuba ngomnye wabo baya kuphumelela"
  28,68,"Ke kaloku iNkosi yakho Idala oko Ithande (ukukudala) nekukhethileyo, Ayikokwabo ukuzikhethela. Uzuko malube kuAllâh Ophakamileyo (kwizithixo) abazayamanisa naYe"
  28,69,Kananjalo iNkosi yakho Iyakwazi oko kufihlakele ezifubeni zabo noko bakuvezayo
  28,70,"Yona nguAllâh; akukho thixo wumbi ngaphandle kwaYo. Iindumiso zonke zifanele Yena ekuqalekeni (kobu bomi) nakuBomi oBuzayo. Isigqibo sokuphetha sesaKhe, kukuYe apho niza kubuyela khona"